## Project Structure

```
src/main/java/{{langConfig.groupId}}.learn/
  Client.java            # Main client class
  HttpClient.java        # HTTP layer with retry logic
  OAuth2Client.java      # OAuth 2.0 implementation
  PaginatedIterator.java # Pagination iterator
  errors/                # Error class hierarchy
  resources/             # One file per API resource
  types/                 # Data model classes
src/test/java/           # Unit tests (JUnit 5)
docs/                    # API documentation per resource
```

## Key Patterns

- Uses `java.net.http.HttpClient` (no external HTTP dependency)
- Jackson for JSON serialization/deserialization
- Builder pattern for client construction
- Methods throw checked `APIError` exceptions
- Path parameters are passed as method arguments
- Query parameters use builder or optional parameter objects

